title: Wolverine v2 102.5 + Alternate Scans (1988-1996|D+S|Mr. Woodman)
description: As promised, here is the low-res scan of the missing special - WOlverine 102.5. This issue was for some reason excluded from both the original source torrent by blackcanary that I used for the v2 collection as well as the massive 5 volume torrent by nemesis43, so now you have it finally available. I have also added alternative low-res Digital rips of the first 5 issues of v2, as well as a high-res version of issue 50 by Mr. Woodman (possibly my favorite issue of Wolverine ever). Thanks to all the scanners, please seed and enjoy! :-)
